WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.890
&gt;&gt; India will not be able to become a superpower
if it does not invest

00:00:04.890 --> 00:00:09.559
seriously in its richest natural resource,
that is, an adolescent girl

00:00:09.559 --> 00:00:13.160
in poverty.
As she becomes the mother of every child of

00:00:13.160 --> 00:00:17.189
the next generation and an
active member of civil society and the business

00:00:17.189 --> 00:00:21.650
world, she will drive
growth and stability and prosperity in this

00:00:21.650 --> 00:00:24.710
country.
It's essential that a girl is not married

00:00:24.710 --> 00:00:29.859
early, pregnant early, HIV
positive, out of the education system.

00:00:29.859 --> 00:00:33.360
If those things happen, there is no way she
can make her contribution

00:00:33.360 --> 00:00:36.760
to the growth of India into a superpower.

